						<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/20 to-slate-900/40 border border-emerald-400/20 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
							<div class="text-emerald-400 text-3xl mb-3">
								<i class="fa-brands fa-aws"></i>
							</div>
							<h3 class="text-emerald-300 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Despliegues en AWS</h3>
							<p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">Despliegue automático de contenedores Docker en AWS tras builds exitosos, con actualización de servicios y tareas.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/20 to-slate-900/40 border border-emerald-400/20 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
