										<span class="text-emerald-400 mt-1">·</span>
										<span>Notificaciones de estado del despliegue</span>
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="border-t border-emerald-400/20 pt-8">
								<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
									<div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
										<span class="text-emerald-400 font-bold">4</span>
									</div>
									<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-300">Gestión de Entornos</h3>
								</div>
